title: 2nd Round Counselling
content: My pessat rank was 1700 but I didnt participate in 1st round of counselling. Is there chances of me getting CSE or CSE (AIML). In any of the 2 branches RR or Electronic city ? Please help.

comments.body: It is highly likely that you could get Aiml but cse core its tough
Highly likely that you'll get AIML at RR and CS core at EC, and maybe even CS core at RR with lots and lots of luck
Aiml rr high probability or ec cse.
